title: 820-00840 20v not run
message:
Fan spins initially then stops then and does not respond to the switch. Capslock does not light up - although one time it lit up for me, but there was the same situation. Sometimes I have seen that it has a backlight. I checked the new good bios and still the same. 
0v  on L7410/20/30 L7210/20 L8410
12.57v  on L7030
5v on L7670
3.3v on L7690
1.2v on L8030
0.9v on L7960
1v on L7900 L8060
1.05v on L7370

title: 820-00840 20v not run
message:
If only missing CPU core voltage, there must be a problem with BIOS, or CPU itself.

Resolder all components in CPU power supply area first; look at pages 54 & 55.
